Certain groups of the Ur-Tarranate Christiac Angelic Human race of Tara received further DNA Bio-Regenesis from the Sirius B Maharaji about 550 million years ago, receiving the genetic enhancement of DNA Strand Templates 13 through 23, then Strand Templates 24 to 48. The 24-48 Strand DNA Template revitalized in the Ur-Tarranate Christiac Angelic Human line is that characteristic to the original Oraphim Angelic Human Race through which the 12-Strand DNA Turaneusiam Angelic Human lineage of Tara had originally been seeded. The genetically enhanced Ur-Tarranates represented a new strain of the Taran Oraphim “Yani” or “Khundara” Eieyani Grail Line, through which the Yanas could incarnate into the Taran drama to initiate further DNA Bio-Regenesis programs among the Fallen Angelic races. The original Oraphim Yani lineage of Tara, known as the “Templar Solar Initiates” had suffered genetic digression through an attempted Bio-Regenesis hybridization program to assist certain Anunnaki Fallen Angelic factions.
